  "text": "Following standard practice in previous work [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] , we use Fscore as the evaluation metric for segmentation, POS tagging and dependency parsing. We report the morpheme-level F-score for Arabic and the wordlevel F-score for Chinese. In addition, we use TedEval [CITATION_3] to evaluate the joint prediction on the SPMRL dataset, because TedEval score is the only evaluation metric used in the official report. We directly use the evaluation tools provided on the SPMRL official website. 8",
